text:
Come for the kitsch, stay for the comfort! We loved the funky decor - so much more personality than a hotel. 

The house and location were perfect - and the back porch was a hit.  Highly recommend the smoothie joint down the block.

Lisa even provided a blow-up mattress to accommodate our 5th person - such a host! Thanks!
title: Eastside Bungalow SXSW/dwntwn
